Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,九点四十一分\NAt 9:41.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:05.45,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,地球的轴心都将为之永远改变\NPlanet's going to shift on its axis line forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.55,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,二十世纪意义最重大的两个事件 \NTwo most significant events in the 20th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.63,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,同盟国大捷 以及这个 \NAllies win the war, and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.24,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,你不会写代码\NYou can't write code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:14.65,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,也不是工程师 \NYou are not an engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:16.57,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,你能做什么 \NWhat do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:19.39,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,乐师演奏乐器 \NThe musicians play the instruments,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:21.07,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,而我指挥管弦乐团\N I play the orchestra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:23.68,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,我在一间小车库里创造出了未来\N I sat in the garage and invented the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:26.81,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,因为设计师必将引领时代 而庸人只知盲目从众 \NBecause artists lead and hacks ask for a show of hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:29.87,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,我欣赏你不在乎一个人能创造多少价值 \NI love this you don't care how much money a person makes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.93,0:00:31.32,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,你在乎他们能创造出什么 \NYou care what they make.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:34.67,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,但你所创造的 并不应代表你的全部 \NBut what you make isn't supposed to be the best part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:36.73,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,只有你 和我用同一种眼光看待世界 \NYou're the only one who sees the world same way I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:41.44,Default,At 9,0,0,0,,没人能和你用同一种眼光看待世界 \NNo one sees the world the same way you do.

